news.title: EWS quarters area must be considered single entity: Karnataka government
news.para: It also said the unused residual floor area ratio (FAR) cannot be transferred to the developer, i.e., M/s Maverick Holdings Ltd.

news.title: East Delhi gets 17 sites for dumping construction and demolition waste
news.para: The civic body has been conducting awareness campaigns to motivate people to keep their areas clean and to not dump garbage or C&D waste in the open.

news.title: Chandigarh civic body to seal 150 commercial properties over tax dues
news.para: As per information, the MC had identified a total of 350 properties which were not paying tax. Taking strict action, the authority served sealing notices and sealed some of these properties too.

news.title: New software for instant patta for subdivided plots in Tamil Nadu
news.para: The land surveyors visit separately to measure and sub-divide the plots. Approximately, 1.5 lakh applications are received every month seeking sub-divisions and there is a huge delay in transferring pattas for sub-divisions.

news.title: New collector rates for Panchkula soon
news.para: For fixing the collector rates for the year 2023, timeline has been drawn for survey and examination of market rates by the tehsil and market committees.

news.title: Ahmedabad civic body seals 290 properties over pending tax dues
news.para: ​​The tax and revenue department sealed the properties of owners whose property tax dues exceeded Rs 50,000. ​​The AMC has prepared a list of about 50,000 such properties with dues exceeding Rs 50,000.

news.title: Dues mount, just 7,800 owe Gurugram civic body Rs 700 crore in property tax
news.para: Revenue from the property tax for the 2022-23 fiscal year was estimated to be Rs 1,100 crore, but MCG has been able to generate only Rs 154 crore in the last nine months.

news.title: E-registration of new realty units picks up pace in Maharashtra
news.para: The number of such developers has gone up to 170 this month from 129 in December 2022.  Six dedicated officers have been appointed to promote and speed up the e-registration scheme that was initiated in October 2021.

news.title: Noida: Five months on, Supertech Emerald Court struggles to free itself
news.para: The haltingly progressing clearance is already running behind schedule, largely because of NCR-wide construction curbs imposed from time to time due to air pollution.

news.title: Government proposes slew of changes to insolvency law
news.para: ​The Insolvency and Bankruptcy Code (IBC), which came into force in 2016, provides for a market-linked and time-bound resolution of stressed assets. The Code has already undergone various amendments.

news.title: Microchip Technology buys 1.68 lakh sq ft office space in Hyderabad for Rs 175 crore
news.para: Microchip estimates that the newly-acquired space will sustain its growth plans for the next 10 years as they continue to hire and expand at a time when other major tech companies have announced layoffs and hiring freezes.

news.title: Kartik Aryan leases luxury apartment in Juhu from Shahid Kapoor
news.para: The actor has paid Rs 45 lakhs as the security deposit for the lease and the rentals will see a 7% escalation every year. In the first year, the monthly rentals will be 7.50 lakh, which will increase to over Rs 8.58 lakh during the third year of the lease.

news.title: Maharashtra RERA to finally monitor recovery warrants' execution
news.para: MahaRERA has set up a dedicated system to monitor the recovery warrant orders pending with 13 district collectorates, including Pune.

news.title: Navi Mumbai: Enkay Garden promoter's properties to be auctioned to recover Rs 6.8 crore
news.para: The Panvel tehsildar's office has announced an auction of various properties of N K Bhupeshbabu, promoter of Enkay Garden, for recovery of around Rs 6.8 crore.

news.title: Income tax department conducts searches on builders in Hyderabad
news.para: Several I-T teams on Wednesday conducted searches on the offices of Oorjita Builders and Developers, Sri Aditya Homes and other firms and their promoters in Jubilee Hills, Banjara Hills, Karkhana, Madhapur, Gandipet and other areas.
